          <text>
            <![CDATA[ <p><strong>National Risk Management Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Homeland Security's Cybersecurity and Infrastructure Security Agency to identify, assess, and prioritize risks to critical infrastructure and requires the President to deliver to Congress a national critical infrastructure resilience strategy designed to address the risks identified. </p>]]>
